title: O'NEILL SUPERFREAK 2013/14
description: The totally insane SuperFreak is now warmer than ever. The wetsuit is built with 100% Superstretch neoprene and FluidFlex™ Firewall in the Front Chest and Back. The 2013 SuperFreak keeps the water out and keeps you warm like no other wetsuit ever offered at this price level. Also for 2013, the Superfreak is available in a hooded model for more extreme conditions. More freaks of nature from your friends at O'Neill.
